comment: [Observable in enhanced video] Curry (DAL) moves his pivot foot after the gather.
Noel (DAL) does not take an additional step after the gather.
Matthews (DAL) makes incidental contact with Dragic (MIA) that does not affect his SQBR.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of MIA possession is overturned and possession is awarded to DAL.
Barnes (DAL) sets the screen on Johnson (MIA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Johnson (MIA) makes marginal contact with Barnes (DAL) that does not affect his FOM.
Johnson (MIA) makes contact to Barnes' (DAL) arm that affects his shot attempt.
The ball is last touched by Curry (DAL) prior to going OOB.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of MIA possession is confirmed.
Dragic (MIA) makes contact with Matthews (DAL) that affects his ability to control the rebound.
[Detectable with stop watch] Waiters (MIA) does not inbound the ball within 5 seconds.
Dragic (MIA) briefly engages with Barnes (DAL) and the contact does not affect his ability to defend Ellington (MIA) during the inbound.
Waiters (MIA) commits a take foul on Matthews (DAL).
Noel (DAL) makes marginal contact with Waiters (MIA) on his drive to the basket.
